### Build Docker Image

```bash
docker build -t civie-chatbot .
```

### Run with Docker Compose

```bash
docker-compose up
```

## Requirements

- Python >= 3.8
- FastAPI
- MongoDB
- Qdrant (Vector Database)
- OpenAI API Key (or compatible LLM service)

